---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Services & Pricing — Bruce Web Development"
  description="Website design and development services for small businesses: new sites, redesigns, and ongoing updates. Every project quoted up front."
>
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl px-5 py-16 sm:px-8 md:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Services</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-prose text-lg leading-relaxed">
      Every project starts with a conversation about what your business
      actually needs — I'll never sell you more website than that.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-x-12 gap-y-10 md:grid-cols-3">
      <section class="flex flex-col border-t border-edge pt-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">New business website</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
          A fast, mobile-friendly site that tells customers what you do, where
          you are, and how to reach you. Includes basic search-engine setup.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-auto pt-6 font-display font-semibold text-sand">
          Starting at $500
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="flex flex-col border-t border-edge pt-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Website redesign</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
          Already have a site that looks dated or loads slowly? I'll rebuild it
          on a modern foundation while keeping what works.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-auto pt-6 font-display font-semibold text-sand">
          Starting at $500
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="flex flex-col border-t border-edge pt-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Updates & maintenance</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
          Content changes, new pages, and keeping things running — so your site
          stays current without you touching code.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-auto pt-6 font-display font-semibold text-sand">
          $80/month
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-12"><a href="/contact/" class="btn-primary">Get a quote</a></p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
